== Usage ==
This template uses the [[:template:Swiss area data|Swiss area data]] template and can convert the values into km² or km² (sq mi) as well as indicate the year of the survey and create a reference.  The format is 

<nowiki>
 {{Swiss area|</nowiki>'''SFOS number'''<nowiki>|</nowiki>'''units='''<nowiki>|</nowiki>'''year='''<nowiki>|</nowiki>'''ref='''<nowiki>}}
</nowiki>

where units can be either 
* km=yes 
* mi=yes

If year=yes then it displays '''(based on the 2004/2009 survey)''' before the value. Year= can be omitted or left blank to display no text regarding the survey

To add an automatic reference:
{|class="wikitable"
! Code || Type 
|-
| ref=m || [[Municipalities of Switzerland|Municipality]] 
|-
| ref=d || [[Districts of Switzerland|District]] 
|-
| ref=c || [[Cantons of Switzerland|Canton]] 
|-
|}

